fields.name: AllowedHeaders
fields.description: The request headers that the origin domain may specify on the CORS request.

fields.name: AllowedMethods
fields.description: The methods (HTTP request verbs) that the origin domain may use for a CORS request.

fields.name: AllowedOrigins
fields.description: The origin domains that are permitted to make a request against the service via CORS.

fields.name: ExposedHeaders
fields.description: The response headers that may be sent in the response to the CORS request and exposed by the browser to the request issuer.

fields.name: MaxAgeInSeconds
fields.description: The maximum amount time that a browser should cache the preflight OPTIONS request.
